{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"23":"Commercial Transactions (Kitab Al-Buyu)"},"section_detail":{"23":{"hadithnumber_first":3326,"hadithnumber_last":3415,"arabicnumber_first":3326,"arabicnumber_last":3415}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3355,"arabicnumber":3355,"text":"। সিমাক (রহঃ) তার সনদে অনুরূপ হাদীস বর্ণনা করেছেন। কিন্তু তিনি بِسِعْرِ يَوْمِهَا বাক্যাংশটুকু উল্লেখ করেননি। তবে পূববর্তী বর্ণনাটি পূর্ণাঙ্গ।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":23,"hadith":30}}]}